snippet.textDisplay: Wow this is crazy!! First of all, renting is almost always done over the internet here in Sweden, you upload your monthly income and contact to the landlord you're currently having. When I studied my boyfriend and I rented a two bedroom apartment 10 min from the city for $900 in a beautiful neighborhood close to the water
